### Class Terminal üß†
```shell
pyimai -[OPTIONS] "[FOR-OPTION]"

Arguments:	           - Description:
    -p, --prompt	      Send a prompt to the AI
    -f, --filepath	      Image path (optional)
    -u, --upload	      Upload image only
    -e, --expiration	  Image expiration time (seconds)
    -k, --key             The API key.
    -v, --version	      Show version
    -h, --help	          Show help
```

### üöÄ Usage (_Class Terminal_)
- üîπSend a normal text prompt (no image required):

```shell
pyimai -p "hello"
```

- üîπAsk the AI about an image:
```shell
pyimai -p "what is this?" -f "photo.jpg" # image must be in directory
```

- üîπ Upload an image and get its public URL:
```shell
pyimai -u "photo.jpg"
```

- üîπ Show version:
```shell
pyimai -v
```
- üîπ Show help:
```shell
pyimai -h
```

